messages.messageBody:
Hi, Kelly. I have another conference question...sorry to be pestering
you like this...I have "conference-on-the-brain" syndrome! I've already
got my hotel room, but in order to pay for the conference...if I fax my
registration form with my credit card info, do I still need to go
through paypal like I would if I registed through e-mail? I'm anxious
to get this all wrapped up asap. Thank you so much for all your hard
work on this. HeidiC.

messages.subject: Re: [AlwaysLearning] conference question again
messages.msgSnippet: In a message dated 5/24/2003 10:00:17 AM Eastern Daylight Time, ... SOS doesn t have credit card capabilities. Yes, you will need to use PayPal for plastic.
messages.messageBody:
In a message dated 5/24/2003 10:00:17 AM Eastern Daylight Time,
ynxn96@... writes:


> I have "conference-on-the-brain" syndrome! I've already
> got my hotel room, but in order to pay for the conference...if I fax my
> registration form with my credit card info, do I still need to go
> through paypal like I would if I registed through e-mail? I'm anxious
> to get this all wrapped up asap. Thank you so much for all your hard
> work on this. HeidiC.

SOS doesn't have credit card capabilities. Yes, you will need to use PayPal
for plastic. Checks are good too.

~Kelly
